  ('disabled-acfc4025-moex-00012', 'disabled-acfc4025', 'disabled-acfc4025-moex-113-156cbda0', 'sub-disabled-acfc4025-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設原始資料是<BBBBBCCCCCCCCAAAAAA>，編碼後的資料是 <B,5,C,8,A,6>，則此編碼方式是採用下列何種方法？', '["Huffmancoding", "JPEGencoding", "Run-lengthencoding", "LempelZiv（LZ）encoding"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:39:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5de56163c9d1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ab19b9b1ea4d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "413", "s": "1412", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-acfc4025-moex-00013', 'disabled-acfc4025', 'disabled-acfc4025-moex-113-156cbda0', 'sub-disabled-acfc4025-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在 TCP/IP 協定堆疊中，最上層為應用層，最下層為實體層。中間三層從 上至下，依序為下列何者？', '["網路層、傳輸層、連結層", "傳輸層、網路層、連結層", "連結層、網路層、傳輸層", "連結層、傳輸層、網路層"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:39:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5de56163c9d1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ab19b9b1ea4d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "413", "s": "1412", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
